Hi Judy,
Check out what I was able to find on the Knowledge Network.
This report shows the success of four cities that made community brands, much like what your county is looking at doing.
http://icma.org/en/icma/knowledge_network/documents/kn/Document/2889/Brandstanding_Four_Cities_Share_Their_Success
Thanks for the question; I hope I was able to help!
Jesse Himes, Knowledge Network Intern, jhimes@icma.org

author: Judy Sage
text:
Is anyone running an online store with County branded merchandise? 
 We need your ideas. 
The County of Placer is currently looking for a vendor who has the capabilities to create an online site;  print, embroider and silk screen merchandise and package and ship merchandise to the end user.
title: Merchandise Ecommerce Store
